parameters: “I wonder if it won’t work if I don’t have it equipped…?”
"Are you going to wear a school swimsuit...?"
“Even though it’s an NPC, it’s too embarrassing…!!”
"But I took the trouble to defeat him..."
“You just have to put it on quickly…!”
"It's embarrassing to wear a swimsuit at someone's house...!!"
“This is what I wanted to see!!”
“After all, school swimsuits are limited to old school clubs!!”
“Regardless of the title, I was able to accomplish the quest!!”
"Does that mean you're getting a little stronger...?"
“With this, it might be okay to expand your range of action a little more…!!”
“It is said that there is a terrible master in the western sewers.”
“I want you to bring me the proof that the owner has.”
